返乡隔离政策至今仍然存在。\n然而人们怕是已经忘记恶意返乡之前的内容是“先隔离后拘留”\n\n![](https://bafkreidwzpiqcs5blszqkduys7myb3fygcpir6bgfdumw3hml3un6bntni.ipfs.hub.textile.io/?filename=2B3C5E46-4B1E-42F8-91CF-ECA0BE366A08.jpeg&filetype=image%2Fjpeg) [加载失败请点击此](https://t-hole.red/ipfs.html#bafkreidwzpiqcs5blszqkduys7myb3fygcpir6bgfdumw3hml3un6bntni)\n\n---\n", "timestamp": 1650415141}, {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": null, "create_time": 1650415005, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1650429831, "likenum": 6, "n_attentions": 6, "n_comments": 8, "pid": 29461, "poll": null, "reply": 8, "text": "# 重磅：维尼🐻挂了！\n![](https://s2.loli.net/2022/04/20/FBUNORXcgI3fa8Z.jpg)\n", "timestamp": 1650415005}, {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": null, "create_time": 1650414877, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1650541402, "likenum": 13, "n_attentions": 13, "n_comments": 26, "pid": 29460, "poll": null, "reply": 26, "text": "无系大一，上学期三门数学课和程设课都是4.0，但其他只有3.6，年级30%，有可能能转贵吗？\n（孩子真的不想学那么多物理😭）", "timestamp": 1650414877}, {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": null, "create_time": 1650414828, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1650426749, "likenum": 3, "n_attentions": 3, "n_comments": 5, "pid": 29459, "poll": null, "reply": 5, "text": "\n![](https://bafkreicq6svon3hqqzgtbcdcw35vkxzp2qoyptdtmnwtthoa6ilhgbsf3q.ipfs.hub.textile.io/?filename=6E4E82F8-C159-4C13-8E1B-0911191E717C.jpeg&filetype=image%2Fjpeg) [加载失败请点击此](https://t-hole.red/ipfs.html#bafkreicq6svon3hqqzgtbcdcw35vkxzp2qoyptdtmnwtthoa6ilhgbsf3q)\n\n---\n"